resources.bingcustomsearchnote_s4: In S4 Tier, you get intelligent query completion capability tailored to your selected domains. Use this Tier along with one of the S1, S2 or S3 Tiers to add intelligent query completion capability to your site search or vertical search experience.
resources.bingcustomsearchnote_s2:
In S2 Tier, you can rank relevant webpages for a given query honoring your custom search instance configuration.  With this tier you also get Statistics feature that can be used to derive insights such as call volume, 
top queries, API response code distribution, and market distribution amongst many others.
resources.bingcustomsearchnote_s3:
In S3 Tier, you can also rank relevant images along with webpages for a given query honoring your custom search
 instance configuration. You also get Statistics feature that can be used to derive insights such as call volume, 
top queries, API response code distribution, and market distribution amongst many others.
resources.bingcustomsearchnote_s1: In S1 Tier, you can rank relevant webpages for a given query honoring your custom search instance configuration. Features like adding sites, blocking sites, pinning sites, instance staging, and instance sharing are easily configured and supported through the authoring portal.
